Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.41,0:00:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Toilet-bound Hanako-kun"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.83,0:01:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Yashiro"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We were forcibly returned from\NWonder Number Three, the Hell of Mirrors,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.25,0:01:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,a world on the other side of mirrors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"Black Canyon"\NIt's been three days since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.37,0:02:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Black Canyon"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.41,0:02:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that we made it back safely,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but I wonder about Mitsuba-{\i1}kun{\i0},\Nthe ghost boy I met in Number Three's Boundary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He was cute, but also cocky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.45,0:02:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, he tried to protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But because of Tsukasa-{\i1}kun{\i0},\Nhe turned into Wonder Number Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.79,0:02:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yay! I'm gonna eat you.\N--I wonder if Mitsuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}\Nwill be safe with him there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Kou-{\i1}kun {\i0}must be worried, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.41,0:02:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kou-{\i1}kun {\i0}told me about Mitsuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}\Nas soon as we got back from the Hell of Mirrors.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.20,0:02:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a ghost... but he's my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But he disappeared once.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd never get to see him again,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.12,0:02:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but, well, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, this is kind of hard to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.87,0:03:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He may have gone with\Nthat Tsukasa guy for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.04,0:03:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kou-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.16,0:03:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.70,0:03:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll figure something out, so it'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.29,0:03:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,After he told me about Mitsuba-{\i1}kun{\i0},\NKou-{\i1}kun {\i0}said that with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.37,0:03:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I have found you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.37,0:03:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...our princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.33,0:03:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Apparition 12:\NThe Little Mermaid"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.29,0:03:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The economic sparring between the Marshall Plan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sigh..."\Nand Cominform over Berlin and the Korean War...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.37,0:04:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, Yashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.16,0:04:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,--What are you doing here?!\N--After Stalin's death, the new leader,\NKhruschev, criticized Stalin's methods
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,--I got a sudden urge to see you.\N--After Stalin's death, the new leader,\NKhruschev, criticized Stalin's methods
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,--What are you talking about?!\N--After Stalin's death, the new leader,\NKhruschev, criticized Stalin's methods
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,--and advocated peaceful\Ncoexistence with the USA.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,--Do you think I'm lying?\N--and advocated peaceful\Ncoexistence with the USA.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,--The sudden rapprochement between the USA\Nand USSR caused consternation in many countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sigh..."\N--The sudden rapprochement between the USA\Nand USSR caused consternation in many countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,--I'm in class, so be quiet, okay?\N--The sudden rapprochement between the USA\Nand USSR caused consternation in many countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.87,0:04:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,--Okay.\N--The sudden rapprochement between the USA\Nand USSR caused consternation in many countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,--Okay.\N--The People's Republic of China\Nwas in an alliance with the USSR and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.45,0:04:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,--Nene-{\i1}chan {\i0}is talking to herself again.\N--The People's Republic of China\Nwas in an alliance with the USSR and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,--So?\N--This included Apollo Program\Nand the Space Race in general.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,--Oh! I just braided that this morning.\N--This included Apollo Program\Nand the Space Race in general.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,--What was on your mind?\N--This included Apollo Program\Nand the Space Race in general.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.25,0:04:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--What was on your mind?\N--It was of course driven my scientific progress\Nand humanity's interest in outer space,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Scribble, scribble"\N--What was on your mind?\N--It was of course driven my scientific progress\Nand humanity's interest in outer space,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.41,0:04:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Scribble, scribble"\N--Fine.\N--It was of course driven my scientific progress\Nand humanity's interest in outer space,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.04,0:04:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"Scribble, scribble"\N--It was of course driven my scientific progress\Nand humanity's interest in outer space,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,--It was of course driven my scientific progress\Nand humanity's interest in outer space,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,--I was thinking that Kou-{\i1}kun{\i0}\Nmight be feeling down.\N--It was of course driven my scientific progress\Nand humanity's interest in outer space,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,--I was thinking that Kou-{\i1}kun{\i0}\Nmight be feeling down.\N--but in the Cold War, rocket technology\Nwas also linked to missiles and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,--Why?\N--but in the Cold War, rocket technology\Nwas also linked to missiles and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,--"Why"?\N--but in the Cold War, rocket technology\Nwas also linked to missiles and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He was friends with Mitsuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure his friend forgetting him\Nmade him feel lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.95,0:04:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if we can do something to cheer him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any good ideas?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.75,0:05:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're only worried about the boy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.91,0:05:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.50,0:05:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hanako-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I was lonely when you got\Nsucked into that mirror, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.83,0:05:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you lonely, Yashiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's not the time, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"Shove"\NAnyway, get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I was worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.50,0:05:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He really was worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,All done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Slide..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.62,0:06:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"Miracle: The Ascension of a Daikon"\N"Crash"\N--Miracle!\N--No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Miracle: The Ascension of a Daikon"\N"Crash"\N--How artistic! The Ascension of a Daikon!\N--No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.33,0:06:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yashiro-{\i1}san{\i0}, please save your\Nmakeover for {\i1}after {\i0}class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.58,0:06:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nene-{\i1}chan{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They say there's a big clock\Nsomewhere in the school, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe different species can't\Nunderstand each other after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"Gulp..."\NNene-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.54,0:06:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What have you fallen in love with this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,An apparition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,An abalone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You always tease me and\Nstick your nose in my business,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but you won't tell me about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.87,0:06:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, sometimes you look so vulnerable,\NI can't just abandon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:07:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it would be better\Nif I were an apparition, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well now, you wish to become an apparition?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.00,0:07:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What a delightful coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall grant your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's talking to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nene-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Look down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I am down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Puffy"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"Puffy"\NIt is a pleasure to make your\Nacquaintance, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Puffy"\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.45,0:07:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Mutter, mutter"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Quietly..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.75,0:07:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dash"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dash"\NNene-{\i1}chan{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the Seven Wonders' boss's assistant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus, I'm friends with a super strong exorcist!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who you are, but if you touch me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Point"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cling"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.91,0:07:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cling"\N...you'll get worse than just burned!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Cling"\NPardon me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,but you aren't terribly convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:07:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yeah.\N--It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:08:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"Sway"\N--Yeah.\N--It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Your Highness, you may remain\Nwhere you are, so please hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We have come to free Your Highness from\Nthe clutches of that loathsome School Wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.87,0:08:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"Five" "Two"\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Five" "Two"\NTo free me from Hanako-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"Five"\N"Seven"\NWhy would you want to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Has Your Highness forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You carry a portion of our mistress\Nthe mermaid's body within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean... that scale?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.70,0:08:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I swallowed that scale\Nthat Hanako-{\i1}kun {\i0}and I are...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It is our law that one who consumes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the flesh and blood of our mistress\Nwill become our next ruler.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness, you are our princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.91,0:08:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.16,0:08:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness is simply gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:09:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans lack discernment,\Nbut if you were to come to our world...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,--Your status as a princess!\N--Nene-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,--Your extraordinary beauty!\N--Nene!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You could hook any man that struck your fancy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Harem"\NYou could hook any man that struck your fancy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"Harem"\N"Gulp..."\NYou could hook any man that struck your fancy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.95,0:09:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"Harem"\N"Gulp..."\NA-Any man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.58,0:09:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"Harem"\N"Gulp..."\NCould you tell me a little--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"Snap"\NCould you tell me a little--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.79,0:09:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Thud"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Thud"\N"Shock" "Shock"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ow..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ow..."\NBesides, this will be better\Nfor Your Highness as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ow..."\NFor me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mental Image" "Tremble"\NFor me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mental Image" "Tremble"\N--I have observed Your Highness for some time,\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mental Image" "Tremble"\Nand that School Wonder's treatment\Nof you is simply beyond the pale!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"Mental Image" "Tremble"\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't even accept the gift\Nyou so graciously gave him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and he even treated you roughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.70,0:09:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He refuses to say anything about himself
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and simply uses Your Highness\Nto his heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That urchin has no regard for\NYour Highness whatsoever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,While she may not look it,\Nour mistress is quite kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:10:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And unlike that urchin,\Nwe love and respect Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Now please, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the mermaid's lifeblood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.08,0:10:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kindly drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.45,0:10:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It will overwrite your unfortunate\Nbond to that School Wonder
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.16,0:10:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and formally establish\Nyour bond with the mermaid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If I drink this, I can cut ties with Hanako-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.00,0:10:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Your body will then no longer\Nchange due to water.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your most unfortunate Highness,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.29,0:10:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,coming with us will bring you happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall return for you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.58,0:10:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give us your answer then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.37,0:10:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.62,0:10:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Girls' Bathroom"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.41,0:11:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Haku-joudai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.95,0:11:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the mermaid's at it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want to lose my cleaner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut ties with someone you're interested in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.41,0:11:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So {\i1}that's {\i0}why you've been acting strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It was because of love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.75,0:11:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you do, Aoi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.29,0:11:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If the other person wasn't\Nthat interested in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"Rumble"\NI'd rather cut off my own head\Nthan cut ties with Ao-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"Rumble"\NA-Akane-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Ao-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Five points.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:11:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Aoi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.50,0:12:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Five... points.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's more than last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Five out of one hundred.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.66,0:12:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He's happy about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You might as well. Go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Number Seven-{\i1}sama {\i0}we're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.12,0:12:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an inconsiderate, willful brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.83,0:12:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I wouldn't go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans and apparitions really shouldn't mingle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Some part of you must realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, that doesn't apply\Nto a good man like Misaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"No. 2\NScience Prep. Room"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"No. 2\NScience Prep. Room"\NHuh? A mermaid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.87,0:12:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,--Why not?\N--What?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Zero hesitation"\N--Why not?\N--What?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--Why not?\N--What?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.00,0:12:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to get you to stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"Princess wanted, no experience necessary,\Nno academic requirements."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a good deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.41,0:12:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"Waah!"\NListen, I'm in trouble here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.37,0:13:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What do Number Seven-{\i1}sama {\i0}and Minamoto say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.66,0:13:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't asked them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I think... I shouldn't bother\NMinamoto-{\i1}kun {\i0}right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.50,0:13:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,With Hanako-{\i1}kun{\i0},\NI never know what he's thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.95,0:13:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,you've known Hanako-{\i1}kun{\i0}\Nfor a long time, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Hanako-{\i1}kun {\i0}in the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's Tsukasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Number Seven doesn't want you\Nknowing that, at least not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he won't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.62,0:13:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why he won't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess he really doesn't trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"Gya ha ha!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Gya ha ha!"\NIt'd probably be inconvenient\Nfor him if you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Gya ha ha!"\NYou're soft on Number Seven-{\i1}sama{\i0}, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.62,0:13:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"Gya ha ha!"\NI mean, donuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"Gya ha ha!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.91,0:13:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Or else,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:14:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe he's afraid of you finding out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, you should make your own decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just make sure you don't regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"No. 2\NScience Prep. Room"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.41,0:14:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Number Seven-{\i1}sama{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Porcupinefish and Un'un"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, give us your answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"Shove"\NI'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Shove"\NI really just can't cut ties with Hanako-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.75,0:14:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"Shove"\NWh-What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how well you'd treat me,\NI can't just leave in the middle of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:15:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Hanako-{\i1}kun {\i0}really is just using me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.83,0:15:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and maybe he really doesn't care about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I want to believe that's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Your Highness, please reconsider!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.75,0:15:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! Show her the pictures!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir, right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Pictures?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.91,0:15:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought Your Highness would like to see\Nthe esteemed gentlemen who will adore you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.29,0:15:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, photos of handsome mermen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.54,0:15:31.79,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.79,0:15:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really interested, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"Swim through a beautiful coral reef with me.\NGrand Duke Angelfish"\N"Come to me. Ambassador Goosefish"\NYes! Fish prints!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,"Fish"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.70,0:15:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,--For a fish as beautiful as Your Highness,\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"Wink"\N--For a fish as beautiful as Your Highness,\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Wink"\N--any man will be yours for the taking.\N--Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.70,0:15:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"Fish"? What do you--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.12,0:15:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, such beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.00,0:16:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What a powerful tail fin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What reserved pectoral fins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And those large eyes,\Nso reminiscent of abyssal darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on, when you called me beautiful,\Nyou meant as a fish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Cast aside your hideous legs and come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.45,0:16:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to the world of fishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No! I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.50,0:16:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness is rash, thick-legged,\Nand a poor judge of males--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.91,0:16:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,an overwhelming loser in the game of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Th-Th-Th-That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.62,0:16:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Part of you must have realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As you are now, you'll never have\Na boyfriend as long as you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"Quake, quake"\NAs you are now, you'll never have\Na boyfriend as long as you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness was merely\Nborn into the wrong world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.50,0:17:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw it all away--both the parched world\Nof the living and your hideous legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you come to our world...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,--...Your Highness will be a queen!\N--Come to me, Nene.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"Her Highness for Life"\N"Ambassador Goosefish"\N--...Your Highness will be a queen!\N--Come to me, Nene.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Grand Duke Angelfish"\N--...Your Highness will be a queen!\N--Nene-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Grand Duke Angelfish"\N--Put simply...\N--Nene-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Prince Beakfish"\N--Put simply...\N--Nene-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.41,0:17:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Top of the popularity pyramid"\N...you'll be popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Top of the popularity pyramid"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.83,0:17:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Popular?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.95,0:17:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, drink this mermaid's lifeblood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.79,0:17:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How nice your world is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,or how bad her life is now don't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yashiro likes me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hanako-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:18:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"Waah!"\NU-Unhand Her Highness, School Wonder!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"Waah!"\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't your mistress ever teach you not to\Ntake things that belong to other people?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get too full of yourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Soy sauce" "Sashimi" "Flutter"\N"Wasabi"\NIf you get too full of yourselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Soy sauce" "Sashimi" "Flutter"\N"Wasabi"\NI'll make sashimi out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.45,0:18:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"Splish-splash"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"Splish-splash"\NMistress!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,"Shock" "Splish-splash"\NMistress!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.95,0:18:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"Shock" "Splish-splash"\NHey, you lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tremble, tremble"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tremble, tremble"\NHow vexing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tremble, tremble"\NWe will never give up, School Wonder!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tremble, tremble"\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.58,0:18:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness, we shall return!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.95,0:18:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hanako-{\i1}kun{\i0}, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't planning to go, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought a harem might be nice, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"Stare..."\NYou thought a harem might be nice, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"Twitch" "Stare..."\NYou thought a harem might be nice, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Twitch" "Stare..."\NS-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:18:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.91,0:18:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a chance to stay human,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and you go and try to turn into an apparition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.58,0:19:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought, if I were an apparition\Nlike you, I could get closer to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, maybe, I'd be able to\Nunderstand you, Hanako-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I know I probably\Ndon't mean anything to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.50,0:19:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so silly, Yashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.75,0:19:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to tell you, but I never did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.79,0:19:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That was... the first time a girl\Never told me she liked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.16,0:20:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...I had a little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed him, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yashiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.04,0:20:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...do you really... want to know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do, then one day...\NI'll tell you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So, stay my assistant until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.58,0:20:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard this rumor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.45,0:20:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,"Broadcast Room"\NHave you heard this rumor?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.70,0:20:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,"Broadcast Room"\NThere are stories of\Nseven wonders in this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.04,0:21:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"Keep Out"\NThere are stories of\Nseven wonders in this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.45,0:21:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you collect all the right stories,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,the cursed seal will be broken, and the\NSeven Wonders of the Occident will attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Frankenstein, the Wolf Man,\NMary-{\i1}san{\i0}, and Backbe--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.66,0:21:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.87,0:21:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't play pranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.41,0:21:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.79,0:21:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That goes for you, too, Natsuhiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.79,0:21:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I just kind of ended up here,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.04,0:21:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,but... is it okay for me to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.04,0:21:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You should decide that\Nfor yourself, Mitsuba-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing, shrimp?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.12,0:22:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of how we should play next.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.70,0:22:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Amane?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.79,0:22:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Confession Tree"\N"He's grown a little since then."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.25,0:22:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Confession Tree"\N"He's grown a little since then."\NBroccoli.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.83,0:22:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Confession Tree"\N"He's grown a little since then."\NBroccoli gratin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.79,0:22:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Kou?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.08,0:22:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he'd stay late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.62,0:22:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait, Mitsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get strong soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.83,0:22:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.79,0:22:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you back from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.54,0:22:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Kou!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.66,0:22:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:22:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.79,0:23:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kou,\NEat these if you like.\NNene"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.33,0:23:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kou,\NEat these if you like.\NNene"\NSummer vegetables?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.25,0:23:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, have you heard about Yousei-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.95,0:23:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.50,0:23:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I carry candy on me every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.45,0:23:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how about...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.91,0:23:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...the way to summon Hanako-{\i1}san {\i0}of the Bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.45,0:23:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I know a few things about Hanako-{\i1}kun{\i0}\Nthat you can't learn from rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.16,0:23:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How kind he is, how dangerous he is, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.12,0:23:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako-{\i1}san{\i0}, Hanako-{\i1}san{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.08,0:23:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.54,0:23:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.70,0:23:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.79,0:23:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Caught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.20,0:23:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there, Yashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.25,0:23:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
